{"tid":1277721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK:外交部拒證實中美元首大阪峰會有否談論香港問題","createTime":"2019-07-02T09:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:40:26.000Z","uid":125193,"like":549,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"16bdb6292270e8c58ff3a4b92aafd31d3312324f","tid":1277721,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"對於美國總統特朗普表示，在大阪二十國集團會議，同國家主席習近平簡短談及香港修訂逃犯條例觸發的示威，在北京，外交部發言人耿爽沒有證實中美元首會晤時，有否談及香港問題，只是指出，中方在香港問題上的立場堅定，美方也是了解。<br />\n<br />\n被問到特朗普說，有些政府不要民主，所指的是中央政府或是特區政府，耿爽表示，應該由美方解釋。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽重申，香港是中國的特別行政區，香港事務純屬中國內政，對有關國家粗暴干涉香港事務和中國內政，表示堅決反對和強烈不滿，並要再次告誡有關國家，要謹言慎行，不得以任何形式，為暴力違法的份子撐腰壯膽。<br />\n2019-07-02 HKT 16:48<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466263-20190702.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466263-20190702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=46bdb697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466263-20190702.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ef433250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466263-20190702.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d5918d0292e19d58b3c2e7f4f8d35b58071ae673","tid":1277721,"uid":4462,"like":535,"dislike":0,"score":535,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"即係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403df659f9961fbb324c3069693bcca4f49b1145","tid":1277721,"uid":125193,"like":218,"dislike":0,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"姐係有lo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7952715bae6ba83c25fc1bfc85aca67f106832b2","tid":1277721,"uid":266805,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"咁即係有"},{"pid":"03ce331df3ca4bfa78af2208453239ea6b99b47b","tid"